The 13 edition of the Safaricom SOYA award was held in Nairobi KICC on Thursday evening. The event brought together sports icon and personalities to celebrate the milestone taken by both merging and established athletes in Kenya.Present as the chief guest was Ethiopia's Haile Gebreselassie,who is currently the Ethiopia athletes president.Also among others who managed to grace the occasion were Politician Esther Passaris,FKF president Nick Mwendwa Safaricom Sylvia Mulinge as well as the SOYA founder Paul Tergat among many others.Olympic 5000M gold holder and 10000 silver Medalist Vivian Cheruiyot was crowned the sports person of the year.